=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n工傷期間叫你離職，係都等你工傷完先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHr都犯例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4dc92374278bd7da90273a0a9ababd0e8c511c","tid":1092268,"uid":47052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T21:01:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/legislat/content1.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Flegislat%2Fcontent1.htm&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJzBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=d3759b8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/legislat/content1.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.onc.hk/zh_HK/can-employment-terminated-employee-suffering-work-related-injuries/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.onc.hk%2Fzh_HK%2Fcan-employment-terminated-employee-suffering-work-related-injuries%2F&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJzBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=5c09b63a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.onc.hk/zh_HK/can-employment-terminated-employee-suffering-work-related-injuries/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上網揾下勞工法例同相關個案啦，再唔明就打個電話去問勞工處。<br />\n<br />\n記得所有野要留底留證據保障自己，無論你追唔追究都好。<br />\n<br />\n其實勞工法例係保障自己，應該每一個都要知同了解，唔係淨係靠hr/人，乜都唔知好易俾人呃。"},{"pid":"526975cba4aa11e2d0a2afd9c1dda7964d1bf194","tid":1092268,"uid":243847,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:24:59.000Z","msg":"大企業黎 我怕報左勞工署 會寫花個履歷"},{"pid":"d94c35d5ec060ddad2d7b799a8514f0f88b4b776","tid":1092268,"uid":243847,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:26:21.000Z","msg":"同埋我懷疑對方跟本無通知勞工署幫我報工傷<br />\n唔係點解敢直接炒人"},{"pid":"f93909453ff57ef05f4165594dd939ba9cd8d7de","tid":1092268,"uid":79481,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"526975cba4aa11e2d0a2afd9c1dda7964d1bf194","tid":1092268,"uid":243847,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:24:59.000Z","msg":"大企業黎 我怕報左勞工署 會寫花個履歷"},"citedBy":0,"replyT